## .NET Build Outputs
# Use ** so nested module projects are covered too — the old src/*/obj/ globs
# only matched one level deep, so every src/Modules/<Area>/<Project>/obj/ was
# silently committed. Those stale assets froze restore state and hid dependency
# drift until a clean restore blew up.
artifacts/bin/
artifacts/obj/
**/bin/
**/obj/

